Empath::

Empath's mental voice still carries a backlash, not because she 
wants it to, but because the Vok artifact has pushed her powers almost 
beyond control.  <There is NOTHING to discuss.  I have waited three 
centuries for this, and I'm tired of waiting.  The Empath you knew was 
nothing but a hollow mockery, a slave to her Galvapred chip!  Now I am 
myself once more, and I will NOT be denied!>
